ActivityEarned: Density of number of transactions made within 1sq.km of the area
MoneyEarned: density of amount of money earned within 1sq.km of the area
AvgTransactionEarned: Average amount of transactions made within the area
CustomerActivity: Average activity (number of transactions) of the area residents
CustomerAvgTransaction: Average transaction amount of the area residents
OutProvinceEarnings: Percentage of the number of transactions made within the area by itês out-of-province visitors
ForeignEarnings: Percentage of the number of transactions made within the area by itês foreign visitors
EarningsDiversity: Number of top business categories (of 76) enough to cover 80% of the total number of transactions got by the area
SpendingDiversity: Number of top business categories (of 76) enough to cover 80% of the total number of transactions made by the area residents
BusinessDensity: Number of active businesses within the area per sq.km
AvgBusinessSize: Average earnings of an active business within the area
